    <item>
      <title>GPG Keys</title>
      <link>https://sumone.xyz/gpg/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://sumone.xyz/gpg/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;If you don&amp;rsquo;t know what gpg key is, Check out an &lt;a href=&#34;https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/GnuPG#Create_a_key_pair&#34;&gt;introduction to gpg🛡️&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Text file of my public GPG key is &lt;a href=&#34;https://sumone.xyz/files/sum.asc&#34;&gt;here🔐&lt;/a&gt;. cv25519 2026-06-24&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To import my key, run the following command one your fav Terminal:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;curl &#39;https://sumone.xyz/files/sum.asc&#39; | gpg --import&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;🧬 Fingerprint is:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;3E09 F8C7 FC2C 8C06 1B51 4E4B 8C5B 35C8 CD92 4311&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
